| Obey script to create the Marathon 1 game
| by building a wrapper app and downloading
| and unzipping the game data

Dir <Obey$Dir>

IfThere ^.!M1A1 Error ^.!M1A1 game directory already exists

wget http://archives2.bungie.org/a1sdl/m1a1_sdl.zip

IfThere m1a1_sdl.zip Then Else Error m1a1_sdl.zip file was not downloaded

aowrapper "Marathon 1" ^.!A1M1

unzip m1a1_sdl.zip -d ^.!A1M1

IfThere ^.!M1A1.M1A1 SDL Then Else Error Failed to unzip m1a1_sdl.zip

Delete ^.!M1A1.data
Delete ^.!M1A1.!Help

Rename ^.!M1A1.M1A1 SDL ^.!M1A1.data

Copy ^.!M1A1.data.ReadMe M1A1 SDL.html ^.!M1A1.!Help

SetType ^.!M1A1.!Help HTML

